    {
      "text": "Imadoki no Vampire: Bloody Bride (いまどきのバンパイアBLOODY BRIDE, Today's Vampire: Bloody Bride), is a PlayStation game published by Atlus Co. Ltd. Japan. Released in 1996 in Japan, it was never officially translated into English.\nBloody Bride in essence is a dating simulation. You play as a young vampire who has reached (vampire) adulthood. He is sent to earth to suck the blood of a girl with a 'platinum aura'. However the girl has to willingly allow him to suck her blood. The character is given three years to complete his mission.",
      "lang": "en",
      "source": "wikipedia_en"
    }
